data.description: Welcome to 1007 Saddle Hill in Marietta, Georgia. This renovated two bedroom, two and a half bath home is nestled in the tranquil swim & tennis community of Mulberry Farms in the heart of East Cobb! With its beautiful painted brick exterior & darling front porch, this home offers a perfect blend of comfort and charm.           As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that moves your eyes throughout the first floor. On your right is your powered bath and coat closet and to the left youCOll immediately notice the oversized, eat-in kitchen. Walking into the expansive kitchen, you see the featured pristine white cabinets with upgraded hardware, stunning granite countertops, and all the light of a fall day shining through the immaculate plantation shutters. Cooking enthusiasts will adore this space, perfect for culinary creations and gatherings.         Next you move into the open-concept living/ dining room which provides an inviting atmosphere, with the cozy fireplace, ideal for relaxation and entertaining. Step outside into your private backyard patio, where you can either grill on a fall day or unwind in peace, enjoying the calm of suburban life.          Upstairs, the oversized master bedroom boasts a tray ceiling, creating a sense of grandeur. The owner's bathroom is equally impressive, with a vaulted ceiling, luxurious jet tub, and a separate shower for a spa-like experience. Plus, there's an expansive walk-in closet, ensuring you have all the storage space you need. The secondary bedroom is nearly as spacious and features an en-suite bathroom, offering both comfort and privacy for guests or family members. Lastly you have your laundry room conveniently located on the second floor.         This townhome style condo is a rare find located in the prestigious Sope Creek, Dickerson, and Walton school district and is just minutes away from East CobbCOs fine dining, shopping, parks & nature trails, and all the amenities you could desire. With easy access to Atlanta, you'll enjoy the convenience of city life while residing in this peaceful suburban community. Don't miss the opportunity to make this wonderful condo your new home. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and elegance in the heart of East Cobb!
